1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:31,490 --> 00:01:36,050
[A Lonely Hero's Journey]

3
00:01:36,210 --> 00:01:38,870
[Episode 18]

4
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:44,930
Warden.

5
00:01:45,090 --> 00:01:45,910
Yizhong?

6
00:01:46,539 --> 00:01:48,120
Why did you come in person for duty today?

7
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:49,979
There's an important prisoner here.

8
00:01:49,979 --> 00:01:52,550
Director Zhou told me to keep an eye on him personally.

9
00:01:52,550 --> 00:01:53,310
This is the prisoner that

10
00:01:53,310 --> 00:01:55,770
Section Chief Xie requested for a handover.

11
00:01:56,550 --> 00:01:57,030
Okay.

12
00:02:01,430 --> 00:02:01,870
Move!

13
00:02:09,340 --> 00:02:10,270
Someone is here.

14
00:02:27,810 --> 00:02:29,240
Please sign here.

15
00:02:29,310 --> 00:02:30,510
Okay. Wait a moment.

16
00:02:48,079 --> 00:02:49,240
Get me Warden Lu.

17
00:02:55,750 --> 00:02:56,350
Hello?

18
00:02:57,100 --> 00:02:57,810
This is he.

19
00:02:59,329 --> 00:03:00,110
Okay.

20
00:03:00,130 --> 00:03:01,770
I'll be right there.

21
00:03:03,780 --> 00:03:04,480
Gu,

22
00:03:04,510 --> 00:03:05,390
something urgent has come up.

23
00:03:05,390 --> 00:03:06,310
I need to go out now.

24
00:03:06,310 --> 00:03:07,270
Please wait a moment.

25
00:03:07,270 --> 00:03:09,000
No rush. Please take your time.

26
00:05:18,150 --> 00:05:19,210
Section Chief Xie.

27
00:05:19,300 --> 00:05:20,330
Where did the gunshot come from?

28
00:05:20,330 --> 00:05:22,190
It seems like it came from inside.

29
00:05:24,870 --> 00:05:26,010
It seems to be inside.

30
00:05:26,010 --> 00:05:26,940
Help!

31
00:05:26,980 --> 00:05:28,580
This gentleman has fainted!

32
00:05:31,830 --> 00:05:32,670
Help!

33
00:05:33,159 --> 00:05:33,770
Hurry!

34
00:05:43,280 --> 00:05:45,140
Hurry. Send him to the infirmary.

35
00:05:48,900 --> 00:05:51,030
Your hands trembled at the wrong time!

36
00:05:52,670 --> 00:05:53,560
Captain Zhang?

37
00:05:58,820 --> 00:05:59,370
Go!

38
00:05:59,400 --> 00:06:00,230
Wait!

39
00:06:04,830 --> 00:06:05,890
Section Chief Xie,

40
00:06:05,940 --> 00:06:07,090
since you’re here,

41
00:06:07,150 --> 00:06:08,150
you can

42
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:10,020
handle this person yourself.

43
00:06:20,980 --> 00:06:22,040
Section Chief Xie,

44
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:23,890
this is the note for you.

45
00:06:45,800 --> 00:06:47,060
It didn't work, did it?

46
00:06:47,270 --> 00:06:49,530
Gu Yizhong is too cunning.

47
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:59,090
It's getting interesting.

48
00:06:59,750 --> 00:07:02,550
Gu Yizhong won't be easy to handle in the future.

49
00:07:02,570 --> 00:07:04,030
As long as we stay focused,

50
00:07:04,230 --> 00:07:05,000
there's nothing in this world

51
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:06,750
we can't handle.

52
00:07:07,470 --> 00:07:09,270
How's our friend from Shanghai?

53
00:07:09,310 --> 00:07:10,290
The people in the infirmary

54
00:07:10,290 --> 00:07:12,750
sent him to Appeasement Military Hospital.

55
00:07:12,950 --> 00:07:14,120
What about the security?

56
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:15,750
A team of ours followed him there,

57
00:07:15,750 --> 00:07:17,420
and there are also two other teams from Shanghai.

58
00:07:17,420 --> 00:07:19,240
It should be fine.

59
00:07:20,940 --> 00:07:22,110
What should we do

60
00:07:22,550 --> 00:07:23,550
about Gu Yizhong?

61
00:07:25,160 --> 00:07:26,360
We'll see how it goes.

62
00:08:15,790 --> 00:08:16,570
Hello?

63
00:08:18,150 --> 00:08:19,600
This is Zhou's Mansion.

64
00:08:25,990 --> 00:08:27,350
Hold on a second.

65
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:30,660
Weng,

66
00:08:31,550 --> 00:08:32,750
it's for you.

67
00:08:33,690 --> 00:08:35,080
It's Mr. Shen.

68
00:08:46,910 --> 00:08:47,770
Hello, it's me.

69
00:08:48,350 --> 00:08:50,030
Appeasement Military Hospital.

70
00:08:50,030 --> 00:08:52,620
Transfer all the men from the Third Brigade here.

71
00:08:52,620 --> 00:08:53,110
Yes.

72
00:08:58,750 --> 00:09:00,020
Where are you going?

73
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:03,230
You can't go out.

74
00:09:04,510 --> 00:09:06,320
Zhifei specifically told me

75
00:09:06,470 --> 00:09:07,910
that you couldn't go out.

76
00:09:19,380 --> 00:09:19,980
Let's go.

77
00:09:24,710 --> 00:09:25,910
So many guns.

78
00:09:27,250 --> 00:09:28,110
Mrs. Zhou,

79
00:09:28,950 --> 00:09:31,280
I've been afraid of guns since I was young.

80
00:09:31,490 --> 00:09:32,270
Are you?

81
00:09:37,510 --> 00:09:38,190
Yes.

82
00:09:38,510 --> 00:09:40,440
I think you're also afraid of guns.

83
00:09:40,950 --> 00:09:43,280
It's better for girls to be afraid of guns.

84
00:09:45,190 --> 00:09:46,070
Open the door.

85
00:09:57,630 --> 00:09:58,470
Bye.

86
00:10:07,560 --> 00:10:09,290
The farther you go, the better.

87
00:10:13,110 --> 00:10:13,910
Hello.

88
00:10:14,770 --> 00:10:15,470
Ji.

89
00:10:15,470 --> 00:10:17,310
Zhou Zhifei, Weng has left.

90
00:10:17,390 --> 00:10:19,140
She pointed a gun at me.

91
00:10:19,960 --> 00:10:22,090
What kind of person did you bring back?

92
00:10:22,110 --> 00:10:23,030
Okay, I got it.

93
00:10:27,190 --> 00:10:28,870
It's time to go home.

94
00:10:29,060 --> 00:10:32,380
[Appeasement Military Hospital]

95
00:10:33,330 --> 00:10:34,460
[Appeasement Military Hospital]

96
00:10:57,910 --> 00:11:00,240
The emergency room is this way. Follow me.

97
00:11:00,340 --> 00:11:00,890
This way.

98
00:11:03,510 --> 00:11:04,070
Come on.

99
00:11:13,790 --> 00:11:15,330
Jiang Boxian is in Ward 5 on the second floor.

100
00:11:15,330 --> 00:11:15,980
Both the first and second floors

101
00:11:15,980 --> 00:11:17,470
are full of people from No. 76 and No. 90.

102
00:11:17,470 --> 00:11:18,210
Got it.

103
00:11:19,830 --> 00:11:21,050
Let's split up.

104
00:11:32,270 --> 00:11:35,600
[Quiet]

105
00:11:37,750 --> 00:11:41,080
Take a good rest, and there won't be anything to worry about.

106
00:11:47,110 --> 00:11:48,060
Be careful.

107
00:11:49,880 --> 00:11:50,600
[Nurse Station]

108
00:11:58,150 --> 00:11:59,250
What are you here for?

109
00:11:59,020 --> 00:12:00,370
[Storage Room]

110
00:12:04,230 --> 00:12:05,160
What's going on?

111
00:12:05,470 --> 00:12:06,550
People downstairs are coming up!

112
00:12:06,550 --> 00:12:07,190
Hurry up and block the door!

113
00:12:07,190 --> 00:12:08,280
They want to kill me!

114
00:12:08,280 --> 00:12:09,700
They're here to kill me!

115
00:12:09,870 --> 00:12:11,670
Scream again, and I'll kill you.

116
00:12:13,030 --> 00:12:13,630
Okay.

117
00:12:16,310 --> 00:12:16,910
Here.

118
00:12:26,260 --> 00:12:26,600
[Ward 7]

119
00:12:40,950 --> 00:12:41,710
[Ward 7]

120
00:12:47,720 --> 00:12:53,990
[Ward 6]

121
00:13:20,510 --> 00:13:21,170
Don't move.

122
00:13:29,240 --> 00:13:31,140
It's me.

123
00:13:32,380 --> 00:13:33,960
Luckily you didn't go in.

124
00:13:34,110 --> 00:13:36,470
There's a bunch of people inside with guns.

125
00:13:36,470 --> 00:13:39,200
If you had gone in, you'd have been shot to pieces.

126
00:13:40,110 --> 00:13:41,200
You've already set up a trap inside,

127
00:13:41,200 --> 00:13:42,230
haven't you?

128
00:13:42,710 --> 00:13:43,630
It's Mr. Li.

129
00:13:49,150 --> 00:13:50,210
What are you doing?

130
00:13:50,270 --> 00:13:51,410
There's a Japanese squad

131
00:13:51,410 --> 00:13:52,650
across the street.

132
00:13:52,790 --> 00:13:54,690
They're probably heading here right now.

133
00:13:54,690 --> 00:13:55,710
If they come,

134
00:13:55,730 --> 00:13:56,920
you won't be able to leave.

135
00:13:56,920 --> 00:13:57,930
Go down from here.

136
00:14:00,560 --> 00:14:01,670
What about Jiang Boxian?

137
00:14:01,670 --> 00:14:02,970
Forget about him!

138
00:14:03,480 --> 00:14:04,860
Run for your life first.

139
00:14:09,010 --> 00:14:10,020
Promise me

140
00:14:10,520 --> 00:14:11,320
you won't die.

141
00:14:12,060 --> 00:14:12,990
Do you hear me?

142
00:14:21,670 --> 00:14:22,340
Come here.

143
00:14:25,710 --> 00:14:26,730
Hurry!

144
00:14:38,660 --> 00:14:39,710
Go.

145
00:14:45,320 --> 00:14:45,730
[Clean]

146
00:14:48,900 --> 00:14:49,550
Director.

147
00:14:49,860 --> 00:14:50,860
What happened?

148
00:14:51,770 --> 00:14:53,350
There were some audacious people who came to take our prisoner.

149
00:14:53,350 --> 00:14:54,550
Do you know where they're from?

150
00:14:54,550 --> 00:14:55,620
I don't know.

151
00:14:56,700 --> 00:14:57,710
We killed five of them

152
00:14:57,710 --> 00:14:58,750
and one escaped.

153
00:14:58,820 --> 00:15:00,710
Take some people to the first floor immediately.

154
00:15:00,710 --> 00:15:02,380
The Japanese are coming over soon.

155
00:15:02,380 --> 00:15:03,770
Hold them off for me.

156
00:15:04,030 --> 00:15:05,850
Don't let them find out where Jiang Boxian is.

157
00:15:05,850 --> 00:15:06,340
Okay.

158
00:15:06,370 --> 00:15:06,900
Let's go.

159
00:15:12,120 --> 00:15:12,600
Who?

160
00:15:13,190 --> 00:15:13,680
It's me.

161
00:15:20,270 --> 00:15:20,940
Director.

162
00:15:29,080 --> 00:15:30,150
Mr. Jiang,

163
00:15:30,520 --> 00:15:31,830
what are you doing?

164
00:15:32,770 --> 00:15:34,270
Sorry, I'm late.

165
00:15:35,120 --> 00:15:37,380
I'm Zhou Zhifei from the Suzhou Station.

166
00:15:41,860 --> 00:15:43,690
So you are Zhou Zhifei?

167
00:15:44,900 --> 00:15:46,840
You're finally willing to see me.

168
00:15:47,250 --> 00:15:49,450
You're even harder to reach than Mr. Li!

169
00:15:49,540 --> 00:15:50,630
That's not true.

170
00:15:51,550 --> 00:15:53,690
I've just been busy.

171
00:15:53,790 --> 00:15:56,260
I'll apologize to you properly another day.

172
00:15:56,350 --> 00:15:58,070
But the situation is urgent,

173
00:15:58,090 --> 00:15:59,870
and we might need to relocate immediately.

174
00:15:59,870 --> 00:16:02,690
[No Smoking, No Noise]

175
00:16:06,230 --> 00:16:07,430
Search all the rooms.

176
00:16:07,580 --> 00:16:08,110
Yes.

177
00:16:10,820 --> 00:16:12,020
I'm not going anywhere.

178
00:16:12,020 --> 00:16:13,320
Do you think

179
00:16:13,350 --> 00:16:15,280
those people outside can save you?

180
00:16:15,430 --> 00:16:17,270
Five people have already died.

181
00:16:18,790 --> 00:16:19,990
Mr. Jiang, you don't want to

182
00:16:19,990 --> 00:16:21,850
sacrifice your comrades, do you?

183
00:16:24,250 --> 00:16:25,980
The Japanese will be here soon.

184
00:16:26,710 --> 00:16:27,390
Fine!

185
00:16:27,410 --> 00:16:28,410
Tell them to come!

186
00:16:28,410 --> 00:16:29,390
Tell them to arrest me!

187
00:16:29,390 --> 00:16:31,120
I'd rather be captured by them!

188
00:16:34,250 --> 00:16:37,120
We're all straightforward people, so let's be honest.

189
00:16:37,120 --> 00:16:38,670
Mr. Li is well aware of your purpose

190
00:16:38,670 --> 00:16:40,290
for going to Shanghai this time.

191
00:16:40,290 --> 00:16:41,240
So he instructed us

192
00:16:41,240 --> 00:16:43,530
not to let you meet with the Japanese.

193
00:16:44,140 --> 00:16:46,420
If Chiang wants to be a traitor,

194
00:16:46,510 --> 00:16:47,870
sorry, he's too late.

195
00:16:49,470 --> 00:16:51,550
The number one traitor in the Kuomintang

196
00:16:51,550 --> 00:16:53,740
is none other than our Mr. Wang.

197
00:17:01,160 --> 00:17:03,450
My purpose for coming to Shanghai this time

198
00:17:03,450 --> 00:17:04,530
is to connect with those

199
00:17:04,530 --> 00:17:06,390
who are capable and committed to resisting the Japanese.

200
00:17:06,390 --> 00:17:07,630
You can save that rhetoric

201
00:17:07,630 --> 00:17:09,270
for the reporters.

202
00:17:19,760 --> 00:17:21,190
Since the start of the resistance,

203
00:17:21,190 --> 00:17:22,670
no central committee member of the Kuomintang

204
00:17:22,670 --> 00:17:23,520
has died.

205
00:17:24,109 --> 00:17:26,290
The word "Xian" in my name means "first."

206
00:17:26,290 --> 00:17:27,619
Just let them arrest me.

207
00:17:28,390 --> 00:17:29,790
I admire that.

208
00:17:57,330 --> 00:17:59,640
I know your wife and child are coming

209
00:17:59,670 --> 00:18:01,070
to Suzhou tomorrow. Is that right?

210
00:18:01,070 --> 00:18:03,000
Don't try to play this game with me!

211
00:18:05,120 --> 00:18:07,090
I've seen this too many times.

212
00:18:09,350 --> 00:18:11,610
The reason they're my family is because

213
00:18:11,830 --> 00:18:13,390
they understand that I'm ready

214
00:18:13,390 --> 00:18:16,050
to sacrifice myself for the country at any time.

215
00:18:16,430 --> 00:18:17,310
I'm one of you.

216
00:18:17,470 --> 00:18:18,490
I'm one of you.

217
00:18:19,060 --> 00:18:19,840
Director.

218
00:18:22,320 --> 00:18:24,410
The Japanese have stormed in.

219
00:18:34,940 --> 00:18:35,890
Mr. Jiang,

220
00:18:36,390 --> 00:18:37,420
there's something

221
00:18:37,420 --> 00:18:38,950
I need to ask for your instructions on.

222
00:18:38,950 --> 00:18:39,710
What is it?

223
00:18:45,350 --> 00:18:46,540
Hurry up.

224
00:18:46,600 --> 00:18:49,870
[Ward 4]

225
00:18:53,390 --> 00:18:57,330
[Ward 6]

226
00:18:58,390 --> 00:18:59,440
What happened?

227
00:18:59,460 --> 00:19:00,080
Just now,

228
00:19:00,120 --> 00:19:01,440
a few reckless members

229
00:19:01,470 --> 00:19:02,350
of the Loyal and Righteous Army

230
00:19:02,350 --> 00:19:03,810
tried to stir up trouble at the hospital,

231
00:19:03,810 --> 00:19:04,870
and we killed them.

232
00:19:04,870 --> 00:19:05,430
Guards!

233
00:19:06,690 --> 00:19:07,970
Have our brothers

234
00:19:06,750 --> 00:19:10,510
[Ward 6]

235
00:19:08,000 --> 00:19:09,470
search the whole hospital immediately.

236
00:19:09,470 --> 00:19:10,590
If any of their people are still around,

237
00:19:10,590 --> 00:19:11,490
kill them on sight!

238
00:19:11,490 --> 00:19:11,990
Yes!

239
00:19:11,520 --> 00:19:12,230
[Ward 6]

240
00:20:09,230 --> 00:20:10,550
How many times have I told you?

241
00:20:10,550 --> 00:20:12,190
You can't save Jiang Boxian!

242
00:20:12,190 --> 00:20:13,370
Why didn't you listen?

243
00:20:13,370 --> 00:20:14,830
Do you know that besides

244
00:20:14,860 --> 00:20:16,110
the people from No. 90,

245
00:20:16,110 --> 00:20:17,150
Mr. Li had two teams

246
00:20:17,150 --> 00:20:18,140
waiting for you at the hospital?

247
00:20:18,140 --> 00:20:20,590
They were just waiting for you to walk into their trap.

248
00:20:20,590 --> 00:20:22,400
I have to complete my mission myself.

249
00:20:22,400 --> 00:20:23,130
Xinping,

250
00:20:23,310 --> 00:20:25,120
you're an experienced comrade.

251
00:20:25,430 --> 00:20:27,190
Can't you stop being so naive

252
00:20:27,210 --> 00:20:29,340
as to carry out such a foolish mission?

253
00:20:31,030 --> 00:20:32,100
In your eyes,

254
00:20:32,160 --> 00:20:33,970
all risks are foolish.

255
00:20:34,270 --> 00:20:35,670
You only know four words:

256
00:20:35,850 --> 00:20:37,030
adapt to the situation.

257
00:20:37,030 --> 00:20:39,360
That's because I don't want to die in vain.

258
00:20:39,390 --> 00:20:40,150
Do you know

259
00:20:40,150 --> 00:20:40,830
what would happen

260
00:20:40,830 --> 00:20:41,790
if you got caught today?

261
00:20:41,790 --> 00:20:43,520
Have you thought about others?

262
00:20:45,470 --> 00:20:46,370
Don't worry.

263
00:20:46,800 --> 00:20:48,070
If I got caught,

264
00:20:48,260 --> 00:20:49,610
I wouldn't drag you down with me.

265
00:20:49,610 --> 00:20:51,730
You're still so self-righteous.

266
00:20:52,060 --> 00:20:53,070
If, as you said,

267
00:20:53,150 --> 00:20:54,420
Jiang Boxian was sent from Chongqing

268
00:20:54,420 --> 00:20:55,240
to negotiate with the Japanese,

269
00:20:55,240 --> 00:20:56,640
then I must take him away.

270
00:20:56,990 --> 00:20:58,150
I can't let Generalissimo Chiang

271
00:20:58,150 --> 00:20:59,640
surrender with Wang Jingwei.

272
00:20:59,640 --> 00:21:01,210
I have to prevent this from happening.

273
00:21:01,210 --> 00:21:02,610
You?

274
00:21:04,140 --> 00:21:05,580
That's ridiculous.

275
00:21:05,740 --> 00:21:07,550
What makes you think you can stop it?

276
00:21:07,550 --> 00:21:09,170
Today they sent Jiang Boxian;

277
00:21:09,170 --> 00:21:11,370
tomorrow they'll send a Wang Boxian or a Li Boxian.

278
00:21:11,370 --> 00:21:12,970
How many people can you stop?

279
00:21:13,790 --> 00:21:15,950
Do you really think you can save the country

280
00:21:15,950 --> 00:21:17,450
and the nation all by yourself?

281
00:21:17,450 --> 00:21:17,940
Yes.

282
00:21:24,030 --> 00:21:25,020
Ou Xinping,

283
00:21:25,670 --> 00:21:28,030
you're as naive as ever.

284
00:21:33,430 --> 00:21:34,030
Of course,

285
00:21:35,550 --> 00:21:36,490
if everyone in the National Government

286
00:21:36,490 --> 00:21:37,730
were like you,

287
00:21:38,550 --> 00:21:39,750
this country

288
00:21:39,870 --> 00:21:42,110
wouldn't have fallen into such a state.

289
00:21:46,610 --> 00:21:48,740
You finally said something sensible.

290
00:21:54,620 --> 00:21:55,220
Okay.

291
00:21:56,940 --> 00:21:58,060
