464
00:31:48,730 --> 00:31:49,540
In five days.

465
00:31:50,080 --> 00:31:51,080
Five days?

466
00:31:52,170 --> 00:31:53,210
Don't panic.

467
00:31:53,840 --> 00:31:54,950
I've thought of a way

468
00:31:54,950 --> 00:31:56,070
to rescue Junxia,

469
00:31:56,750 --> 00:31:57,880
but I can't

470
00:31:57,980 --> 00:31:58,830
