They're experts in digging tunnels.

581
00:37:40,180 --> 00:37:40,780
Remember,

582
00:37:41,070 --> 00:37:42,870
my surname is Sha and yours is Lu.

583
00:37:50,660 --> 00:37:51,990
[Xiangfusi Lane]

584
00:37:57,470 --> 00:37:58,070
Take it.

585
00:37:58,510 --> 00:37:59,190
Don't move.

586
00:38:12,470 --> 00:38:13,110
Here.

587
00:38:35,750 --> 00:38:37,060
What?

588
00:38:37,220 --> 00:38:39,220
That's what you call professional.

589
00:39:27,360 --> 00:39:28,680
Yizhong! Yizhong!

590
00:39:31,570 --> 00:39:32,430
Vice Director.

591
00:39:37,200 --> 00:39:38,260
Have some peanuts.

592
00:39:39,150 --> 00:39:42,880
I heard something happened at the Appeasement Military Hospital.

593
00:39:43,660 --> 00:39:44,700
What happened?

594
00:39:46,640 --> 00:39:47,630
The night before last,

595
00:39:47,630 --> 00:39:49,350
No. 76 sent someone

596
00:39:49,350 --> 00:39:50,270
to our dungeon.

597
00:39:51,210 --> 00:39:52,470
You really don't know?

598
00:39:55,710 --> 00:39:57,170
Let me show you something.

599
00:40:01,790 --> 00:40:03,590
This is the resume of Ou Xinping,

600
00:40:03,670 --> 00:40:05,930
who was Zhou Zhifei's old flame

601
00:40:06,110 --> 00:40:08,230
back when he was in the CBIS.

602
00:40:06,590 --> 00:40:07,030
[Ou Xinping]

603
00:40:07,030 --> 00:40:10,160
[Position: Head of the Suzhou Operation Zone, CBIS]

604
00:40:10,390 --> 00:40:11,250
Vice Director,

605
00:40:12,110 --> 00:40:13,970
you really have a way with things.

606
00:40:15,790 --> 00:40:17,790
Quite a few people at No. 76 know her.

607
00:40:18,470 --> 00:40:19,610
This Ou Xinping

608
00:40:19,350 --> 00:40:21,460
[Ou Xinping] [Position: Head of the Suzhou Operation Zone, CBIS]

609
00:40:19,740 --> 00:40:21,550
is a seasoned CBIS agent,

610
00:40:22,550 --> 00:40:25,580
one of the so-called "20 Arhats" who helped build the CBIS from the ground up.

611
00:40:25,580 --> 00:40:26,670
Arhats?

612
00:40:30,180 --> 00:40:31,740
Because of Zhou Zhifei,

613
00:40:32,150 --> 00:40:34,390
Xu Enzeng sent her back to Suzhou this time,

614
00:40:34,390 --> 00:40:37,110
with the goal of pulling Zhou Zhifei back in.

615
00:40:40,810 --> 00:40:41,600
No way.

616
00:40:43,750 --> 00:40:46,610
Is there anything that's impossible for us agents?

617
00:40:47,090 --> 00:40:48,550
Yizhong, don't forget,

618
00:40:48,990 --> 00:40:50,140
agents

619
00:40:50,510 --> 00:40:52,590
serve political purposes.

620
00:41:11,510 --> 00:41:12,370
Vice Director,

621
00:41:13,340 --> 00:41:14,940
are you kidding me?

622
00:41:15,240 --> 00:41:16,580
The photo is so blurred.

623
00:41:17,240 --> 00:41:18,710
Look, which one of these two

624
00:41:18,710 --> 00:41:19,670
is she?

625
00:41:21,480 --> 00:41:22,830
This one.

626
00:41:23,910 --> 00:41:25,870
The person is a bit hard to make out,

627
00:41:26,950 --> 00:41:29,020
but you can tell by the height, build,

628
00:41:29,050 --> 00:41:29,850
and demeanor.

629
00:41:34,920 --> 00:41:36,990
Zhou Zhifei didn't teach you these—

630
00:41:37,020 --> 00:41:37,620
thank you—

631
00:41:38,090 --> 00:41:39,350
during your training?

632
00:41:43,990 --> 00:41:45,390
This Zhou Zhifei.

633
00:41:46,720 --> 00:41:48,180
I'm telling you, Yizhong,

634
00:41:48,350 --> 00:41:50,150
identifying a disguised person

635
00:41:52,670 --> 00:41:53,910
requires more than just looking at

636
00:41:53,910 --> 00:41:55,150
their appearance.

637
00:41:55,870 --> 00:41:57,190
I'm inexperienced

638
00:41:57,750 --> 00:41:59,810
and still have a lot to learn from you.

639
00:42:03,550 --> 00:42:04,410
Vice Director,

640
00:42:05,040 --> 00:42:06,300
what should we do next?

641
00:42:10,990 --> 00:42:12,150
It won't take long

642
00:42:12,930 --> 00:42:14,310
before I expose her.

643
00:42:14,400 --> 00:42:16,560
[Vice Director's Office]

644
00:42:15,610 --> 00:42:18,840
I have dispatched all the personnel of the Intelligence Station.

645
00:42:18,840 --> 00:42:20,790
But she's a seasoned CBIS agent,

646
00:42:21,010 --> 00:42:23,410
so it won't be that easy to catch her, right?

647
00:42:25,730 --> 00:42:26,720
Yizhong,

648
00:42:26,980 --> 00:42:28,980
don't forget my background.

649
00:42:29,970 --> 00:42:30,970
I'm from the NBIS.

650
00:42:35,160 --> 00:42:36,820
Let me reveal a bit more.

651
00:42:37,170 --> 00:42:38,580
Chief Wan Lilang

652
00:42:38,750 --> 00:42:40,310
has assigned

653
00:42:40,390 --> 00:42:41,900
a team from No. 76 to me,

654
00:42:42,470 --> 00:42:44,400
which is under my unified command.

655
00:42:45,270 --> 00:42:47,010
They are stationed at Xinsu Hotel.

656
00:42:47,010 --> 00:42:48,290
Two of them

657
00:42:48,670 --> 00:42:49,750
know this Ou.

658
00:42:50,670 --> 00:42:52,070
Not to mention Arhats,

659
00:42:52,590 --> 00:42:54,150
even Sun Wukong wouldn't escape.
